WEBVTT

00:05.440 --> 00:06.680
Supper time!

00:06.720 --> 00:07.800
Those leaves and twigs
that you boiled up this morning?

00:07.840 --> 00:09.720
It's called Bramble-Beard Soup.

00:09.760 --> 00:11.080
Have you noticed

00:11.120 --> 00:13.320
that I am not able to walk
for more than 50 paces

00:13.360 --> 00:14.840
without stopping
for a crap?

00:14.880 --> 00:16.280
It's an acquired taste.

00:16.320 --> 00:17.480
You'll get used to it.

00:17.520 --> 00:19.960
You made a deal with my enemy.

00:20.000 --> 00:23.200
Antedia's army is standing by
if this doesn't work out,

00:23.240 --> 00:24.400
and you want me
to trust you?

00:26.320 --> 00:28.920
Do you want to bed her
before she dies?

00:28.960 --> 00:31.920
Here's some advice...
keep an eye on your husband.

00:31.960 --> 00:34.160
Send word to the Regni.

00:34.200 --> 00:36.600
They can start their siege.

00:36.640 --> 00:37.640
Do you trust him?

00:37.680 --> 00:39.120
Not as far as I
could shit him.

00:39.160 --> 00:41.880
I think I know
why the Romans came.

00:41.920 --> 00:45.720
Lokka, the Great Earth Demon,
has come to destroy you.

00:45.760 --> 00:47.240
Seize them!

00:47.280 --> 00:48.160
Guards!

00:48.200 --> 00:49.320
Protect the Queen!

00:49.360 --> 00:50.560
You have made a big mistake
here today.

00:52.120 --> 00:55.160
Together,
we must destroy Lokka.

00:55.200 --> 00:56.400
Together?

00:56.440 --> 00:59.680
They are singing
your name, sister.

00:59.720 --> 01:02.320
The dead are singing
your name!

01:02.360 --> 01:03.280
It turns out

01:03.320 --> 01:05.880
you're not a
pointless, annoying,

01:05.920 --> 01:07.400
interfering little
pain in the ass.

01:08.760 --> 01:10.240
Thank you.

